# AI4MT-experiment

This repository contains the results of the experiments with the AI4MT framework:

* Folder [experiments/mr\_inference\_experiment](./experiments/mr_inference_experiment) contains both the gotten programs generated by the MR inference task and the models (and its execution traces) used to analyse their semantic validy.
* Folder [experiments/follow\_ups\_experiment](./experiments/follow_ups_experiment) contains the follow-up models generated for the case studies (data centres, autonomous vehicles, DFAs)
